@%META:TOPICINFO{author="EelcoVisser" date="1080168064" format="1.0" version="1.4"}%
%META:TOPICPARENT{name="HotSpots"}%
My [[http://personalwebs.oakland.edu/~grossman/erdoshp.html][Erdös number]] is at most 5:

	* Erdös (0)
	* Csiszar (1)
	* [[http://136.199.54.185/%7Eley/db/indices/a-tree/l/Longo%3AGiuseppe.html][Giuseppe Longo]] (2) 
	* [[http://136.199.54.185/%7Eley/db/indices/a-tree/m/Moggi%3AEugenio.html][Eugenio Moggi]] (3)
	* [[http://136.199.54.185/%7Eley/db/indices/a-tree/b/Benaissa%3AZine=El=Abidine.html][Zino Benaissa]] (4)
	* [[http://136.199.54.185/%7Eley/db/indices/a-tree/v/Visser%3aEelco.html][Eelco Visser]] (5)

At least according to Dave Clarke who wrote "My Erdos number is 5 ([[http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/indices/a-tree/c/Clarke%3ADave.html][Clarke]], [[http://136.199.54.185/%7Eley/db/indices/a-tree/j/Jay%3AC=_Barry.html][Jay]], Moggi, Longo, Csiszar, Erdos).".
(But DBLP does not confirm the link Clarke/Jay nor the link Longo/Csiszar.)

-- Main.EelcoVisser - 23 Mar 2004

Dave writes:
For the record, the Longo/Csiszar connection can be found on [[http://personalwebs.oakland.edu/~grossman/Erdos2][Erdos2]]. I can confirm the Clarke/Jay paper:  Exploiting Shape in Parallel Programming. C B Jay, D Clarke, J Edwards. IEEE Second International Conference on Algorithms and	Architectures for Parallel Processing, June 1996. http://citeseer.ist.psu.edu/jay96exploiting.html

-- Main.EelcoVisser - 24 Mar 2004

-----------------------------------------
------+++ Root: Shela (6)

My [[http://personalwebs.oakland.edu/~grossman/erdoshp.html][Erdös number]] is at most 6:

According to the [[http://personalwebs.oakland.edu/~grossman/Erdos2][Erdos2]] list

	* Erdös (0)
	* Saharon Shela (1)
	* Amir Pnueli (2)

According to DBLP

	* [[http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/indices/a-tree/a/Apt%3AKrzysztof_R=.html][Krzysztof R. Apt]] (3)
	* [[http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/indices/a-tree/b/Bergstra%3AJan_A=.htmlJan Bergstra]] (4)
	* [[http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/indices/a-tree/k/Klint%3APaul.html][Paul Klint]] (5)
	* [[http://136.199.54.185/%7Eley/db/indices/a-tree/v/Visser%3aEelco.html][Eelco Visser]] (6)

Here is a part of the search tree

	* SHELAH, SAHARON (1)
	* Pnueli, Amir (2)
		* Willem P. de Roever (3)
